featured_reviews.review_id: Masaajid Allah ka ghr hain...koi bhi shakhs kisi bhi school of thought se taaluq rakhta hu masjid me Allah ki ibaadat ka haq rakhta hai....masjid kisi shakhs ki malkiyat nahi hai...ye tu Allah ka ghr hai....par nihayaat afsoos k saaath mujhe ye likhna par raha hai k meri garri ka nuqsaaaan or mery joootyka nuqsaaan sirf isi liye kia gea q k me maktba ehl e hadees se taaluk rakhta hn.....ye wesi hi baat hai jesay k kuch jahil looog kisi oor firqy ky logooon ki nimaz parhny ki jaga kooo dhooty hai.....Allah pak hidaayat naseeb kry essy logoon ko...Ameen
